      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.hubeali": [
          "Muhammad Bin Yahya, from Muhammad Bin Al Husayn, from Muhammad Bin Sinan, from Ammar Bin Marwan, from Jabir, ",
          "(It has been narrated) from Abu Ja’far<sup>asws</sup> having said: ‘The Hajj is completed by meeting the Imam<sup>asws</sup>’."
        ],
        "en.sarwar": [
          "2. Muhammad ibn Yahya has narrated from Muhammad ibn al-Husayn from Muhammad ibn Sinan from ‘Ammar ibn Marwan from Jabir who has said the following: “Abu Ja’far, ‘Alayhi al-Salam, has said, ‘Meeting the Imam is completion of al-Hajj.’” "
        ]
      }
